lead_paragraph: Logan Couture scored the only goal of the shootout to lead the San Jose Sharks to a 3-2 comeback victory over the Nashville Predators on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Couture Lifts Sharks to 3-2 Shootout Win Over Predators
